{"tid":598584,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"魚子醬無敵好食推薦！！！","createTime":"2018-03-19T15:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T23:46:10.000Z","uid":162829,"like":6,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d3229cbf61c0118c1ce8ab4c1419a560b0cb98c1","tid":598584,"uid":162829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:47:26.000Z","msg":"魚子醬比人一種貴格唔飽既感覺，無錯！的確係！但更多既人係未食過好食既魚子醬先會有咁既評價<br />\n<br />\n本人身為魚子醬既愛好者在此與諸位分享食左返唔到轉頭既魚子醬！<br />\n<br />\n魚子醬係13世紀係俄羅斯只係家常小菜，自從傳入歐洲先變為高級食品<br />\n<br />\n以往係餐廳食覺得好難食，亦因為價錢貴好少再嘗試，直至一次朋友送左盒比我，我返唔到轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/19/233410_d9834c4b7ef9103316ed7a3e014f21a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F19%2F233410_d9834c4b7ef9103316ed7a3e014f21a1.jpg&h=e6f9eda1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上面就係朋友送比我個盒魚子醬，但圖係上網偷既。餐廳垃圾無得同呢盒野比，魚子醬放左入口後，用舌頭逐粒頂爆佢，強烈既奶油香係口內爆發！個刻我真正感受到魚子醬比歐洲人搞到咁貴既原因，係呢個世界上無其他食物可以做到同樣效果！<br />\n<br />\n然後我問朋友盒野洗唔洗二千蚊，咁餐廳食一篤5克都成兩三舊水啦，咁大盒我估二千掛。點知，佢答我800hkd!!! <br />\n<br />\n無乜野分享到，自己說不上大師！但係，我只希望大家睇完呢個post<br />\n<br />\n咪。撚。再。幫。趁。垃。圾！<br />\n<br />\n朋友送比我盒野個網: <a href=\"http://royalcaviarclub.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Froyalcaviarclub.com&d=yCTaMrpfOZ6CYUu1fmQGLwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=d45ff83d\" target=\"_blank\">royalcaviarclub.com</a>"},{"pid":"1ed6e4c4a9d81d27c7501bd2e3b23400726ccd11","tid":598584,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"09a9f5b785c4b9202ef7cb5a567a68505b97672f","tid":598584,"uid":45431,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"八舊水既買過啦，最基本款，黑龍江養殖呀嘛，唔好講到驚為天人咁啦，咪又係一般料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6a363ecee6eba5e1033432a04ed71d8e31e01b","tid":598584,"uid":162829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"好多錯別字，激動得制！抱歉！"},{"pid":"6ce77f6437a62493ba35c8bd60939852f964c793","tid":598584,"uid":162829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>八舊水既買過啦，最基本款，黑龍江養殖呀嘛，唔好講到驚為天人咁啦，咪又係一般料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除左邊到產，要睇埋魚卵幾年，咩鱘魚種，咩水質，攝取方法，呢盒野既魚源條條8-10年。巴打係咪又買伏野啊"},{"pid":"509b60b838860f00e119c3321641ed91eccf234c","tid":598584,"uid":162829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:54:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n咁都俾人屌。。。"},{"pid":"5d8ac5d6a5b61df6bfffdbc45f136a655ee64179","tid":598584,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦伍寶，我直接跟批發商拎，你估街貨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食得既梗係知乜貨，但唔會係你講到咁神囉，係吹奏既至少去到beluga啦"},{"pid":"ac9ef22543dca955c0e2ea08582f955c699f5ec0","tid":598584,"uid":137912,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:57:20.000Z","msg":"打手..."},{"pid":"75e8bac825be6628afaadbc01e9683f323c609fd","tid":598584,"uid":33259,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:58:01.000Z","msg":"魚子醬一人一罐，你當我茂利呀宜家？"},{"pid":"393b637dfdd2cf452695c4cced4e484d313aaf0a","tid":598584,"uid":89240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T15:59:14.000Z","msg":"我係莫斯科100美金一盒都唔知有冇好食"},{"pid":"aec5a5cd132a7561caa625c498b3c586e686986a","tid":598584,"uid":105888,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:00:09.000Z","msg":"做打手做到咁低質<br />\nBlacklist左你間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e83383b8b20e19c0123952b5c4bcbb6c60e9e09","tid":598584,"uid":159236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"呢個post有潛質做royal桃2.0"},{"pid":"c3616ccc34a58e28b3e6582a5d6c90218e127e85","tid":598584,"uid":162829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-